phase2.explanation:
рҹӨ– **Common theming mistakes and how to fix them.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Hardcoded colors | Use `MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primary` |
| No MaterialTheme | Wrap all composables in MaterialTheme |
| Inconsistent colors | Use theme colors everywhere |
| Wrong text color | Use `onSurface` or `onPrimary` |
| No dark theme | Support both light and dark |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use theme colors
Text(
    text = "Hello",
    color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primary
)

// 2. Wrap in MaterialTheme
@Composable
fun MyApp() {
    MaterialTheme {
        Text("Hello")
    }
}

// 3. Theme colors
Button(
    onClick = {},
    colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(
        containerColor = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primary
    )
) {
    Text("Button")
}

// 4. Use onSurface
Card(
    colors = CardDefaults.cardColors(
        containerColor = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.surface
    )
) {
    Text(
        text = "Text",
        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurface
    )
}

// 5. Support dark theme
@Composable
fun MyTheme(
    darkTheme: Boolean = isSystemInDarkTheme(),
    content: @Composable () -> Unit
) {
    val colorScheme = if (darkTheme) darkColorScheme() else lightColorScheme()
    MaterialTheme(colorScheme = colorScheme) {
        content()
    }
}
```

